Package gpp.model.languageparser.java

Class JavaLanguageParser

java.lang.Object
gpp.model.languageparser.LanguageParser
gpp.model.languageparser.java.JavaLanguageParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGeneralLanguageParser, IGeneralLanguageParserConditional, IGeneralLanguageParserExpression, IGeneralLanguageParserFlow, IGeneralLanguageParserLoop, IJavaLanguageParser
public class JavaLanguageParser
extends LanguageParser
implements IGeneralLanguageParserConditional, IGeneralLanguageParserLoop, IGeneralLanguageParserExpression, IGeneralLanguageParserFlow, IJavaLanguageParser
Clase que se encarga de parsear ficheros Java.
